summary: Extends the Honeyside dock and adds some Nightingale Flare.
descriptionHtml:
This is just an extension of the dock connected to Honeyside in Riften.  It adds no new functionality, it\'s just there to look cool.  Nightingale/Nocturnal fans should like it.

Install:
Add plug-in NightingaleDock to C:\\Program Files (x86)\\Steam\\steamapps\\common\\skyrim\\Data

Unintall:
Remove plug-in NightingaleDock from C:\\Program Files (x86)\\Steam\\steamapps\\common\\skyrim\\Data

Notes:  This was my CK learning project.  I learned i have a love-hate relationship with navmesh.
After all is said and done i believe i got the navmesh down.  Please inform me of any issues, as of now I see none.
